wish to 想做某事
We wish to apologize for the late arrival of this train. 我们要为这次火车的晚点表示歉意。
I wish to speak to him alone. Can you arrange that? 我想和他单独谈谈。你能安排一下吗？
Do you wish to say anything, John? 你有话要说吗，约翰？
Many people helped the Thompsons after their house burned. 在托马森的家被烧了之后，很多人都伸出了援手。
They wish to thank everyone who helped them. 他们希望向每个帮助过他们家的人表达真诚的谢意。